        "text": "Ow great website; thanks a lot for sharing. I see you are the author of it; amazing work! Great to see the older pieces of work as well.\n\nWould be interesting to have a small ideas initiative as well; since I have some scrappy prototypes that are interesting to get feedback on\/share\/compare to other approaches which are trying to prototypes little parts of the bigger ideas.",
